title: #92Noon Vox In The Box! Boudreau/Mileski/Walz/Gorg/Lombardi/Ramsey
description: PA and Nordo are in the Xcel Energy Center for Vox In The Box! The FAN's Brandon Mileski co-hosts the first hour of the show when Wild Head Coach Bruce Boudreau stops by! Also, Wes Walz talks Wild hockey, Kevin Gorg previews Hockey Day Minnesota, Michael Lombardi talks about Championship Sunday, and Rachel Ramsey brings in the Distraction Factor!
